Boxed In!: Space voyagers get caught in a Roach Motel.
They Don't Call Him Lucky Sam for Nothing!: "Lucky" Sam Flake gets stranded on an alien transport.

Dust Devil: The Devil tries to make a deal with a Kansas drought damaged town.
